playgamehelp0:
Solitaire Cooking Tower allows you to manage restaurants with many different style of cuisines by playing solitaire.

First, let's begin with basic solitaire rules.
playgamehelp1:
The area where cards are placed in 7 columns is called the 'tableu'.
You can tap or drag the cards in the tableu to move them and arrange them in the descending order, 'K' being the highest and 'Ace' being the lowest.
playgamehelp2:
However, the black and red suites must alternate when arranging them.
Only Ks can be placed on empty columns.
If there aren't any cards to move around tap the card pile to draw more cards.
playgamehelp3: The 4 empty areas on top are called the 'foundation'. You can start stacking the cards of the same suite in ascending order starting with the 'Ace'.
playgamehelp4: Once you complete a round of solitaire you can unlock menus with the points you earned. When you unlock all the menus in the restaurant, you can open up a new restaurant.
playgamehelp5:
The combo gauge will be filled for consecutive points earned.

Activate the combo ability by acquiring 5 combo pieces. Once the combo ability is activated, try and stack as many cards as possible on the foundation within 10 seconds and earn stars!
playgamehelp6: You can get more card decks with 'stars' you earn. Remember that different card decks have different perks.
playgamehelp7:
Hooray! You've reached the end of the tutorial.
Now you can play solitaire and build a variety of restaurants. Good luck!
